   <script type="text/javascript">
    var destination = 'Grüner Grund 15, 32429 Minden'
 function showRoute() {
     var start = document.getElementById("address").value;
     var dest_url = "http://maps.google.de/maps?saddr="+start+"&daddr="+destination;
     window.open(dest_url, '_blank');
 }
 function codeAddress()
 {
 geocoder = new google.maps.Geocoder();
 var latlng = new google.maps.LatLng(-34.397, 150.644);
 var myOptions = {
 zoom: 11,
       mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.HYBRID,
 center: latlng,
 }
 map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("map_canvas"), myOptions);
 address= 'Grüner Grund 15, 32429 Minden';
 backupaddress= 'Grüner Grund, 32429 Minden';
 geocoder.geocode( { 'address': address}, function(results, status) {
 if (status == google.maps.GeocoderStatus.OK) {
 map.setCenter(results[0].geometry.location);
 var marker = new google.maps.Marker({
 map: map,
 position: results[0].geometry.location
 });
         var coordInfoWindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({
         content: "<div style='min-height:0px'><h3>Planen Sie Ihre Anfahrt zu uns</h3>Bitte geben Sie Ihre Adresse an<br/>und drücken Sie dann &quot;anfahrt planen&quot;<br/><input id='address' type='textbox' value='' style='width:200px; border: 1px solid black;-webkit-border-radius: 2px;-moz-border-radius: 2px;border-radius: 2px;'>&nbsp;<input type='button' value='anfahrt planen' onClick='showRoute();'></div>",
         map: map,
         position: results[0].geometry.location
         });
 }
 else if(status == google.maps.GeocoderStatus.ZERO_RESULTS) {
 console.log('call backup');
 geocoder.geocode( { 'address': backupaddress}, function(backupresults, status) {
 map.setCenter(backupresults[0].geometry.location);
 var marker = new google.maps.Marker({
 map: map,
 position: backupresults[0].geometry.location
 });
         var coordInfoWindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({
         content: "<div style='min-height:0px'><h3>Planen Sie Ihre Anfahrt zu uns</h3>Bitte geben Sie Ihre Adresse an<br/>und drücken Sie dann &quot;anfahrt planen&quot;<br/><input id='address' type='textbox' value='' style='width:200px; border: 1px solid black;-webkit-border-radius: 2px;-moz-border-radius: 2px;border-radius: 2px;'>&nbsp;<input type='button' value='anfahrt planen' onClick='showRoute();'></div>",
         map: map,
         position: backupresults[0].geometry.location
         });
 });
 }
 });
 }
   </script>

   <script>
    $("#hpCarousel").on("slide.bs.carousel", function (e) {
     if(typeof(sessionStorage) == 'undefined')
       return false;
     sessionStorage.setItem("carouselitem",$(e.relatedTarget).index());
   });
 
   $(document).ready(function() {
     carouselitem=sessionStorage.getItem("carouselitem");
     if(carouselitem==null)
       sessionStorage.setItem("carouselitem",0);
 
     carouselitem=parseInt(sessionStorage.getItem("carouselitem"));
     if(carouselitem==0)
     {
       $('#item1').addClass("active");
       $('#indicator1').addClass("active");
     }
     if(carouselitem==1)
     {
       $('#item2').addClass("active");
       $('#indicator2').addClass("active");
     }
     if(carouselitem==2)
     {
       $('#item3').addClass("active");
       $('#indicator3').addClass("active");
     }
     if(carouselitem==3)
     {
       $('#item4').addClass("active");
       $('#indicator4').addClass("active");
     }
     if(carouselitem==4)
     {
       $('#item5').addClass("active");
       $('#indicator5').addClass("active");
     }
   });
   </script>

             $('.dropdown').on('mouseenter', function() {
               isSafari = navigator.vendor.indexOf("Apple")==0 && /\sSafari\//.test(navigator.userAgent);
               if(($('#mobilemenu').css("display")=='none'))
               {
                 menu=$(this).find('.dropdown-menu');

                 height=$(this).height();
                 line=$(this).position().top/height;
                 if(line==0)
                   menu.css('top',height);
                 else
                   menu.css('top',height*2);
                 if(isSafari && isyammcontent) // hack for false Safari width detection!
                 {
                   menu.css('left','15%');
                   menu.css('transform','none');
                 }
                 menu.stop(true, true).show();
